title: (Fri Full) Jason Aldean Reveals The Expensive Gift An Artist Gave Him + Lunchbox Has A Beef with a Country Artist!
itunes:title: (Fri Full) Jason Aldean Reveals The Expensive Gift An Artist Gave Him + Lunchbox Has A Beef with a Country Artist!
description:
Jason Aldean stops by to talk about his new album, Eddie seeing him at Chuck E. Cheese, his biggest failure of his career and the expensive gift he was given by another artist. Lunchbox reveals why he has a beef with a certain country artist. Is it justified?
